ts/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"最慘好多都係個價唔會郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ddbffa1f02642ed6a6c6a5d487b9f036892fac","tid":2446280,"uid":359847,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:51:35.000Z","msg":"短短 11 年間，比特幣由冇價值升到今日超過 30 萬一粒。啱啱開始嘅時候，用屋企嘅電腦就可以輕易挖到好多比特幣，但係去到今日，比特幣已經需要耗費大量電力先可以挖掘，而且會損耗電腦。<br />\n<br />\n為咗令到大眾都可以挖礦，美國史丹福大學加密貨幣教授 Dr. Nicolas Kokkalis 同博士團隊合作喺 2019 年研發咗手機挖礦程式 Pi Network，每 24 小時只需要登入噤制一次，個 App 唔會喺背景運行，所以絕對唔會嘥電，唔會損耗電腦。<br />\n<br />\nPi Network 累計已經達到超過 40,000,000 全球用戶，挖礦速度已經由最初嘅 0.8 Pi／小時降速 4 次到今日嘅 0.1 Pi／小時，當用戶數目達到上階段 10 倍嘅時候，Pi Network 嘅挖礦速度就會減半、最終喺達到 10 億或者上主網嘅時候暫停供應。<br />\n<br />\n雖然現時未可以將 Pi 換成法定貨幣，但係研發團隊計劃將會喺今年年尾上市主要加密貨幣交易所，令貨幣可以流通。<br />\n<br />\n如果想趁仲有得挖礦嘅時候攞多啲 Pi 幣，可以喺 App Store／Google Play下載 Pi Network，也可以在官方主網下載：<a href=\"https://minepi.com/，填寫邀請碼【nicksonkwok】獲得\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fminepi.com%2F%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%AB%E5%AF%AB%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E7%A2%BC%E3%80%90nicksonkwok%E3%80%91%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%97&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=7b9521ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://minepi.com/，填寫邀請碼【nicksonkwok】獲得</a> 1 Pi 同加快挖礦速度 25%。<br />\n<br />\n除咗 Pi，建議您可以下載埋 Bee Network，一個由香港人喺 2020 年 12 月研發、運作模式同 Pi 相似、已經有 80 萬用戶嘅挖礦 App。下載連結：<a href=\"https://bee.com/en，填寫邀請碼【nkbee】獲得\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbee.com%2Fen%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%AB%E5%AF%AB%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E7%A2%BC%E3%80%90nkbee%E3%80%91%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%97&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=2b8096b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bee.com/en，填寫邀請碼【nkbee】獲得</a> 1 Bee 同加快挖礦速度 25%。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－<br />\nFAQ:<br />\nQ1：Pi／Bee 係咪騙局？<br />\nA1：Pi／Bee 雖然暫時未能夠換成其他貨幣，但係勝在有龐大嘅用戶網絡，為佢帶來非常大嘅認受性。由於挖 Pi／Bee 只需要投入每日嘅幾分鐘嘅時間，而且唔使畀錢，所以風險好低，即使 touchwood 未能夠上市，亦都唔會令你有任何金錢上嘅損失。反而如果成功，就會令你嘅財富增值。"},{"pid":"b829945bf5f7516b9eee1a10423188a5ca7bd657","tid":2446280,"uid":34996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0944f6368769957e6ae475ea3bc046a16fd50d7f","tid":2446280,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bdac5abc83bb1fd76ecd307626d780d67f8a631","tid":2446280,"uid":62714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d94cebfc1d26aae78f19d5f7a37c363e088a28d","tid":2446280,"uid":114110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"其實聽講買完放番比平台收息，一年袋成30％ 之前有新聞講，堅定流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁人人都李嘉誠啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"咁高息係因為少人玩，一多人玩就唔會有呢個息<br />\n同埋有其他風險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"最高息應該係價值<br />\n日息 30% 玩左一個星期到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"玩過最高息係金條<br />\n最高80幾90%一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b615b5f891e8b6610ff666dbe3da86aff14999","tid":2446280,"uid":148508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dbc22290a85863a2b4568ab67d62b2fdc5d7906","tid":2446280,"uid":49342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c43f07892c79e28727e8f3ffbf03ca34fcb2bda4","tid":2446280,"uid":114110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"634852954c6129c84d116ebf9bbd32a83a87fc30","tid":2446280,"uid":49342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"Defi平台黎，你去binance 買左usd穩定幣先再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"我之前係apex買過eth同bitcoin<br />\n但係平台執q左，仲有幾百蚊拎唔番出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 